      • getRecordIndexFilename

        protected static String getRecordIndexFilename(String tableName)
        Returns the name of the Variable-length Index File associated with a specified table name. Note that this does not determine whether or not the index exists, it simply returns the abstract file name of the index.
        See MIL-STD-2407, section 5.3.1.2 DIGEST Part 2, Annex C.2.3.1.2
        Parameters:
        tableName - the table name to return an index name for.
        Returns:
        the name of a variable-length index file associated with the table name.,
